==Italian==
===Etymology===
Latin ''decidere'' from ''[[de-]] + [[caedere]]''
===Verb===
'''decidere''' [[transitive]]
#To [[decide]] on something
#To [[settle]] or [[resolve]]

====Synonym====
*[[definire]]

'''decidere che''' [[transitive]]
#To decide that something ...

'''decidere''' [[intransitive]]
#To decide, to make up one's mind

===Related terms===
*[[decisione]]
*[[decisivo]]
*[[decisorio]]

===Derived terms===
*[[decidersi]] - to come to; to make up one's mind

